Edit Comment

 

You can edit a comment by clicking on the comment options and choosing the Edit Comment. In the new dialog window that appear you can change the content of the comment.

Delete Comment

 

By clicking on the action you can remove the comment from the system. Ones removed the comment can't be restored

Resolve / Restart Comment

 

When you choose the Resolve Comment action the comment can't be changed and you can't reply to it.

To make all of the actions available again click on the Restart Comment Action
